      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">采菽.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>采菽采菽，筐之筥之。君子來朝，何錫予之？
雖無予之，路車乘馬。又何予之？玄袞及黼。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>They gather the beans, they gather the beans,
In their baskets, square and round.
The princes are coming to court,
And what gifts have I to give them?
Although I have none to give them,
There are the state carriages and their teams.
What more have I to give them?
The dark-coloured upper robes with the dragon,
And the lower garments with the hatchet.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">xiaoya-yuzao-002</prop>
