      <prop type="x-segment-type">stanza</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">stanza</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·002.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">采菽.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>觱沸檻泉，言采其芹。君子來朝，言觀其旂。
其旂淠淠，鸞聲嘒嘒。載驂載駟，君子所屆。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Right up bubbles the water from the spring,
And they gather the cress about it.
The princes are coming to court,
And I see their dragon flags; —
Their dragon flags moving in the wind,
While the sound of their bells comes liwuy-liwuy.
There are the two outside horses, there are the whole teams, —
Proofs that the princes are come.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">xiaoya-yuzao-002</prop>
