      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·002.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">采菽.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>維柞之枝，其葉蓬蓬。樂只君子，殿天子之邦。
樂只君子，萬福攸同。平平左右，亦是率從。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the branches of the oaks,
How abundant are the leaves!
To be rejoiced in are the princes,
Guardians of the regions of the son of Heaven.
To be rejoiced in are the princes,
Around whom all blessings collect.
Discriminating and able are their attendants,
Who also have followed them hither.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-002__005__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
